You just have to create a file in a temp directory : 
```
final Directory systemTempDir = Directory.systemTemp;
final File tempFile = File('${systemTempDir.path}/image_database.imgdb');

// create tempfile
await tempFile.create();
```
and then you have to save the content of the imgdb into the temp file. 
I will add this to the documentation tomorrow. 
In the future it will be possible to pass the path of the imgdb file as an argument to the ArCoreView
Hope i could help.
